    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Characidium tapuia: A. holotype, UFPB 11604, 32.1 mm SL, Brazil, Maranhão, Loreto, Fazenda Fogoso, rio Balsas, rio Parnaíba basin; B. paratype, UFRN 2871, 30.0 mm SL, Brazil, Piauí, rio São Gonçalo do Gurgueia, rio Parnaíba basin, photographed alive." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2605836/files/figure.png" ;
