<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2605838>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Paratypes of Characidium tapuia: A. UFPB 9423, 24.8 mm SL, Brazil, Maranhão, Loreto, Fazenda Fogoso, creek tributary of rio Balsas at the road between Loreto and Buritirana; B and C. MZUSP 98568, 22.0 and 19.2 mm SL respectively, Brazil, Piauí, Santa Filomena, Riacho Recreio, tributary of rio Parnaíba." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2605838/files/figure.png" ;
