<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2605840>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Pseudotympanum of Characidium tapuia: UFRN 2871, 30.0 mm SL, paratype. Number corresponds to the pleural ribs of the 5 th and 6 th vertebrae. Left side, anterior to left." ;
